# --- Entry gesture description ---
msgid "URL Announcer command layer. Press A announce, C copy, S share link, X security, W share menu, R history, M bookmark, B bookmarks, L shorten, T title, E email, O open, P clipboard, D domain check, Q QR code, H help, Escape cancel."
msgstr ""

# --- Layer announce messages ---
msgid "URL Announcer: A announce, C copy, S share link, X security, W share menu, R history, M bookmark, B bookmarks, L shorten, T title, E email, O open in browser, P clipboard URL, D domain check, Q QR code, H help, Escape cancel."
msgstr ""

